Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After I arrived in Tokyo a few days ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I've been waking up to an unusual sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need to repeat myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to not use anything\Nwith my name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheapskate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you show some mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}NINA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps me with the hangovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I ask you if you yesterday\Nif you wanted some for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}was{\i0} drunk, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you hear back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy to get back a\Nplace you just stopped renting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- And your job? \N - Same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.36,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got things to take care of on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}2: THREE NOCTURNAL CREATURES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This looks more like a hospital than a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's private tuition after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:03:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9}80 PEOPLE HAVE BEEN ACCEPTED INTO REPUTABLE COLLEGES!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You coming here every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I don't have that kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ADMISSION FORM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to study a lot on my own\Nto get into a good university.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanna go to uni?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, no, not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...dropping out of educatio\Nnonly leads to trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And those who "told you so"\Nwill relish in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But oh well, that's none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you have time to rehearse, it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free in the evenings and weekends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you'll need to get a job too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Form a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- You said so, right?\N- I said no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please... let's flip them off together!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't do that in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just meant we should focus\Non our respective paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't saying that I wanted to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me with my studies, you with your music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that what you meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought some things didn't add up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets really packed even this late, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoken like a bumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as you put in the effort to study,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you still wanna try forming a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not saying you should learn an instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, you'd make a great singer, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? A singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the voice, and especially the heart for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, to me a band...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a gathering place for people\Nwho have a lot of things they want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Folks crying out things like "I wanna be loved",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"This world sucks",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't with everything anymore",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"I love myself", or "I hate myself"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted to go solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so too at first,\Nbut I miss being in a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much gossip, arguing,\Nand tension that you gotta hold in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,while pretending everything's perfect.\NBut since you're always together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there comes a point where you\Ncan't keep it up and just explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single positive, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But still... it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Creating something with others\Nthat you never could on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll probably get home faster from this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... shockingly rural for being in a city, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the appeal of this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your place is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And there should be a super nearby. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as paying back my share of rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- But... \N- I said don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it in the fridge for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'll warn you, I'm not much of a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you can cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say I don't hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, knife, knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit like composing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You chop the veggies while the water boils.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You prepare the sauce and let it simmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You juggle many different things,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but you bring them all together to form a cohesive whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this knife sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't have any other knives...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to apologize for stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But it reminds me that I'm\Nunable to do anything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never make it living alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you think it's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. I'm very much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can do is just force your way through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Through all the struggles, bothers, and realizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}FLIP THEM OFF!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And keep trying 'till you get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Buying actual plates would be a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}TO DO LIST{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, food's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll need to add buying a lamp too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna just... eat like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do come from a stacked family after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something rich folks would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, we're actually a pretty normal home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... how to put it, a bit strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how we have family precepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Precepts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, like house rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly: the family should always eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Family precepts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly: you shouldn't use your phone in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirdly: every Sunday the family should gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually word got out in class about the type of household I was in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it prided itself in its strictness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I can see where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that I couldn't go\Nback to school, so I had to drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0}'s why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the most popular girl at my school.\NA real beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All the boys were flocking at her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what, she bullied you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she just hates me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you didn't stand up for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl made sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She had enough friends so no one could touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She even had her friends ignore me and bully me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I even had to go to the hospital once, and yet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,both my teachers and parents just told me to stop being problematic-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat. Before it overcooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I like my vegetables well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you really are cut out for singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What you just said, that's like five songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I wanted to try out\Na band where I don't do the vocals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to focus on what I\Ncan communicate through my guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dropping out of high school?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'd be throwing away your future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you changed your\Nmind later, it'll be too late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just need to get into a university, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll study on my own if I must!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If I don't keep up with my studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and get into a university, then my life's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Over, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I don't mean it {\i1}that{\i0} way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that if I don't, I'll have\Nto admit I was always wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To my bullies, teachers, and parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask again then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said, no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got beer left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, that's heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, they're books.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry the big ones, you can go get the lighter ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm fine.\NWill one trip be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, this is the last of the big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you check if I forgot anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta study again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll probably be needing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know how\Nto play it to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it would be\Nbetter off in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh? Are you sure you don't need my help? \N- Don't worry, it's oaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess there's one\Nlast favor you could do me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a big place for a city...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tamagawa River, you've heard of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bigger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought Tokyo had places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo's on the other side over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Close, but not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the edge of Tokyo, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Abut that favor you needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to hear you sing one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Any song you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And to wish you good luck with your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading back to my old place, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you're ever free, let's\Ngo grab a bite together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your\Nmusic too, Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll make a song you can be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And please don't forget to\Nkeep flipping them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could raise your pinkie\Nrather than your middle finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it were up to you, would you keep going?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This void feeling, this eternal feeling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of answers that lead to superficial clichés.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if my fingers tremble...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no right answers,\Nthere's no giving in,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My whole life, I've just been me.\NThat's all there is to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter how much I fight from here on,\Ntomorrow isn't set in stone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"Jim told her to not give up."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even amidst the darkness,\NI'm sure a ray of hope will someday..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta buy a new lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}GIRLS BAND CRY.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's where it gets complicated: the right pronoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was so fun!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got two at the same time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- No way! \N- I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't talked to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't talked to anyone all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you finished unloading?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, all done. My back's killing me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't push yourself too hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We should meet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE WEATHER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}FROM: MOMOKA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have you bought a lamp yet?\NI've got a spare if you need it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you! I would love to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I come get it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, should be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, you came rushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially all of a sudden like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over there. Hopefully it should do the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. As long as it can light up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Have you settled in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you came this far,\Nwanna go grab a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a job back, so I'll treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the famous Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the lamp from Awa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my new drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Awa Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...Uh, I'm Iseri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru, wanna join us? You'll have to pay your share, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You cheapskate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not made of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, actually, I'll just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Nina's new to Tokyo after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru's your age, you'll get along great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, what a big pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've added too many veggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cabbage loses all its flavor\Nif you boil it too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what music do you like, Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Any favorite bands or vocaloids?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me she likes old Showa music,\Nwhich she got from her grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh? Nice! I like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Any favorites?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, "favorite" is a strong word...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are they playing {\i1}Glarech{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You listen to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been to their concerts twice,\Nand once at a festival too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Like the one in Chiba? \N- The very same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They totally sucked though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they suck that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they've amounted to nothing since.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since, they haven't showed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even realize they were gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if everyone loved them at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan, have you ever been to a concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, can I add meat to the pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then try talking to her a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying hard to be friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean she's being forced to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I get where you're coming from, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know anything about you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just... I feel like I'm being talked down to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She goes to a prestigious acting school,\Nit's just her way of speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not trying to be mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what a great person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's even willing to pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To act nice with such an inferior like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just being biased!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's gonna talk to you if you keep up that attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed to never have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be alone for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks for this.. \N- You're... welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She already has what she\Nneeds more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just trying to be nice
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying to get to know me, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass! Moron! Imbecille!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- You shut up! \N- What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,SHUT UP!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wa-wait... stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,SHUT UP!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,GO AWAY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even fix a light on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed to stay in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never getting out of this darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, we really\Nshould form that band.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru...-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should hide your double key better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you already ruined the lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you Nina, I love your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you gain by lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a walking paradox of negativity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's because you're simply\N too honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a coward, but you refuse to ever give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've helped me remember what I forgot,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The things I hold deeply and cherish the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And why I sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you don't have to feel sorry for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.61,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Take all that pain, and inject it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...into music!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,, 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}NEXT: UNORTHODOX Q&A.{\i0}
